  "texts": [
    "For MNIST dataset, due to a small image size, the first max pooling layer in VGG16 was omitted.",
    "In this case, there are two fully connected hidden layers containing 512 neurons each.",
    "For CIFAR10 and CIFAR100 the convolutional layers are followed by only one fully connected hidden layer containing 512 neurons, yielding 15 layers in total.",
    "Finally, for PLACES365, there are two fully connected hidden layers with 4096 neurons each.",
    "The spiking implementation of max pooling operation was done as in ref. 41."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}